<Layout title="BiomEdit — Styleguide">
<div class="sg-intro">
  <p class="overline">Living reference</p>
  <h1>Styleguide</h1>
  <p>The full decided system — colors, tokens, typography, buttons, the Pipeline component, and utility text styles. Sections mirror the original working doc so nothing gets lost as it evolves here.</p>
