  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">1</span><h2>Brand Colors</h2></div>
      <p class="section-sub">Five colors, one family. Deep Blue and Teal are locked to the logo; Ember Orange, Green, and Amber round out the palette. Specific roles get decided as we work through actual page designs.</p>
      <div class="color-grid">
        <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--color-navy);"></div><div class="swatch-info"><div class="name">Deep Blue</div><div class="hex">#2B3682</div></div><div class="role-tag">Locked</div></div>
        <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--color-teal);"></div><div class="swatch-info"><div class="name">Teal</div><div class="hex">#0369B2</div></div><div class="role-tag">Locked</div></div>
        <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--color-orange);"></div><div class="swatch-info"><div class="name">Ember Orange</div><div class="hex">#DA6A2A</div></div><div class="role-tag">Confirmed</div></div>
        <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--color-green);"></div><div class="swatch-info"><div class="name">Green</div><div class="hex">#16A34A</div></div><div class="role-tag">Confirmed</div></div>
        <div class="swatch-row"><div class="swatch" style="background:var(--color-amber);"></div><div class="swatch-info"><div class="name">Amber</div><div class="hex">#F59E0B</div></div><div class="role-tag">Confirmed</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">2</span><h2>Neutral Palette — Cool</h2></div>
      <p class="section-sub">The confirmed direction. Full 100–900 ramp, subtly blue-tinted.</p>
      <div class="ramp-strip9">
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-100);color:#000;">100<span class="hex-lbl">F1F3F6</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-200);color:#000;">200<span class="hex-lbl">E2E5EA</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-300);color:#000;">300<span class="hex-lbl">CBD0D9</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-400);color:#000;">400<span class="hex-lbl">AAB1BE</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-500);color:#fff;">500<span class="hex-lbl">868D9E</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-600);color:#fff;">600<span class="hex-lbl">666D7E</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-700);color:#fff;">700<span class="hex-lbl">4A5161</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-800);color:#fff;">800<span class="hex-lbl">333846</span></div>
        <div class="ramp-swatch" style="background:var(--cool-900);color:#fff;">900<span class="hex-lbl">1C1F28</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">3</span><h2>Color Tokens — Light Theme</h2></div>
      <p class="section-sub">Primary, secondary, and tertiary text and background, built from the cool ramp above.</p>
      <div class="token-grid">
        <div class="token-card">
          <p class="sub-label" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Text</p>
          <div class="token-swatch-row"><div class="token-chip" style="background:var(--cool-900);"></div><div><div class="token-name">Primary</div><div class="token-hex">Cool 900 — #1C1F28</div></div></div>
          <div class="token-swatch-row"><div class="token-chip" style="background:var(--cool-700);"></div><div><div class="token-name">Secondary</div><div class="token-hex">Cool 700 — #4A5161</div></div></div>
          <div class="token-swatch-row" style="margin-bottom:0;"><div class="token-chip" style="background:var(--cool-500);"></div><div><div class="token-name">Tertiary</div><div class="token-hex">Cool 500 — #868D9E</div></div></div>
        </div>
        <div class="token-card">
          <p class="sub-label" style="margin-bottom:14px;">Background</p>
          <div class="token-swatch-row"><div class="token-chip" style="background:#FFFFFF;"></div><div><div class="token-name">Secondary (surface)</div><div class="token-hex">White — #FFFFFF</div></div></div>
          <div class="token-swatch-row"><div class="token-chip" style="background:var(--cool-100);"></div><div><div class="token-name">Primary (canvas)</div><div class="token-hex">Cool 100 — #F1F3F6</div></div></div>
          <div class="token-swatch-row" style="margin-bottom:0;"><div class="token-chip" style="background:var(--cool-200);"></div><div><div class="token-name">Tertiary (recessed)</div><div class="token-hex">Cool 200 — #E2E5EA</div></div></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">4</span><h2>Color Tokens — Dark Theme</h2></div>
      <p class="section-sub">Inverse of the light tokens, plus lightened variants of every brand and accent color for sufficient contrast against dark backgrounds. Deep Blue's dark-mode variant was adjusted to a brighter, more saturated blue — the original white-mixed tint was reading too close to lavender.</p>
      <div class="dark-panel">
        <h3>Programmable biologics for animal health.</h3>
        <p class="body">A protein-engineering and fermentation platform built to move from target to field faster than legacy discovery pipelines allow.</p>
        <div class="dark-token-grid">
          <div class="dark-token-card" style="background:var(--cool-800);"><p class="token-name" style="color:var(--cool-100);">bg-secondary</p><p class="token-hex" style="color:var(--cool-400);">Cool 800 — #333846</p></div>
          <div class="dark-token-card" style="background:var(--cool-700);"><p class="token-name" style="color:var(--cool-100);">bg-tertiary</p><p class="token-hex" style="color:var(--cool-300);">Cool 700 — #4A5161</p></div>
          <div class="dark-token-card" style="background:var(--cool-900);border:1px solid var(--cool-700);"><p class="token-name" style="color:var(--cool-100);">bg-primary</p><p class="token-hex" style="color:var(--cool-400);">Cool 900 — #1C1F28</p></div>
        </div>
        <p class="sub-label" style="color:var(--cool-400);margin-bottom:14px;">Brand &amp; accent — dark-mode variants</p>
        <div class="dark-accent-grid">
          <div class="dark-accent-chip" style="background:var(--color-navy-dark);"><p class="name">Deep Blue</p><p class="hex">#5A94F2</p></div>
          <div class="dark-accent-chip" style="background:var(--color-teal-dark);"><p class="name">Teal</p><p class="hex">#74ADD5</p></div>
          <div class="dark-accent-chip" style="background:var(--color-orange-dark);"><p class="name">Ember Orange</p><p class="hex">#EBAD8A</p></div>
          <div class="dark-accent-chip" style="background:var(--color-green-dark);"><p class="name">Green</p><p class="hex">#7FCC9B</p></div>
          <div class="dark-accent-chip" style="background:var(--color-amber-dark);"><p class="name">Amber</p><p class="hex">#FACA79</p></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="section-head"><span class="section-num">5</span><h2>Typography — PT Sans</h2></div>
      <p class="section-sub">Headings and body both in PT Sans. Pull quotes and captions use PT Sans Italic. Fraunces is reserved separately — see open questions.</p>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">5.1 — Type scale</p>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">Display / H1</span>90px</div><p class="scale-sample" style="font-size:90px;">Engineered biology</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">H2</span>67px</div><p class="scale-sample" style="font-size:67px;">Engineered biology</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">H3</span>51px</div><p class="scale-sample" style="font-size:51px;">Engineered biology</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">H4</span>38px</div><p class="scale-sample" style="font-size:38px;">Engineered biology</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">H5</span>28px</div><p class="scale-sample" style="font-size:28px;">Engineered biology</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">H6 / Body Large</span>21px</div><p class="scale-sample" style="font-size:21px;">Engineered biology</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">Body</span>16px</div><p class="scale-sample body-weight" style="font-size:16px;">Engineered biology for animal health.</p></div>
        <div class="scale-row"><div class="scale-meta"><span class="role">Caption</span>12px</div><p class="scale-sample body-weight" style="font-size:12px;color:var(--text-tertiary);">Engineered biology for animal health.</p></div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">5.2 — Combo</p>
        <div class="combo-card">
          <svg class="mini-logo" width="78" height="17" viewBox="0 0 164 40"><use href="#biomedit-logo" xlink:href="#biomedit-logo"></use></svg>
          <p class="combo-eyebrow">Platform</p>
          <p class="combo-h">Programmable biologics for animal health.</p>
          <p class="combo-body">A protein-engineering and fermentation platform built to move from target to field faster than legacy discovery pipelines allow.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

