      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">8.1 — Overline / Eyebrow</p>
        <p class="sub-desc">Same pattern as the Pipeline's stage labels. Sits above a heading or section to give it context.</p>
        <div class="util-card">
          <p class="util-overline">Platform Overview</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">8.2 — Table styles</p>
        <p class="sub-desc">Header and cell text pulled directly from the Pipeline's column-header treatment.</p>
        <div class="util-card">
          <table class="util-table">
            <thead>
              <tr><th>Code</th><th>Focus</th><th>Category</th><th>Stage</th></tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr><td>BE-101</td><td>Pathogen Protection</td><td>Chronic Disease</td><td>Regulatory Approval</td></tr>
              <tr><td>BE-07</td><td>AMR</td><td>Infectious Disease</td><td>Candidate Optimization</td></tr>
              <tr><td>BE-105</td><td>Methane Reduction</td><td>Sustainability</td><td>Candidate Optimization</td></tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">8.3 — Data label &amp; meta pairs</p>
        <p class="sub-desc">The same bold-label-plus-muted-caption pattern as each Pipeline card's code and focus area — useful anywhere a key value needs a quiet secondary line under it.</p>
        <div class="util-card">
          <div class="data-pair-row">
            <div class="data-pair"><span class="util-data-label">BE-101</span><span class="util-meta">Pathogen Protection</span></div>
            <div class="data-pair"><span class="util-data-label">6</span><span class="util-meta">Active Programs</span></div>
            <div class="data-pair"><span class="util-data-label">3</span><span class="util-meta">Regulatory Pathways</span></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">8.4 — Badges &amp; tags</p>
        <p class="sub-desc">Same shape as the Pipeline's filter tabs, in a non-interactive form — for status flags, category tags, or table-cell labels.</p>
        <div class="util-card">
          <div class="badge-row">
            <span class="util-badge" style="background:var(--bg-tertiary);color:var(--text-secondary);">Draft</span>
            <span class="util-badge" style="background:rgba(3,105,178,0.12);color:var(--color-teal);">Infectious Disease</span>
            <span class="util-badge" style="background:rgba(43,54,130,0.12);color:var(--color-navy);">Chronic Disease</span>
            <span class="util-badge" style="background:rgba(218,106,42,0.12);color:var(--color-orange);">Sustainability</span>
            <span class="util-badge" style="background:rgba(22,163,74,0.12);color:var(--color-green);">Active</span>
            <span class="util-badge" style="background:rgba(245,158,11,0.12);color:var(--color-amber);">Pending</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection">
        <p class="sub-label">8.5 — Form styles</p>
        <p class="sub-desc">Label, input, helper text, and an error state. No dedicated error/danger color exists in the palette yet — Amber is standing in here, worth a real decision once forms are actually being built.</p>
        <div class="util-card">
          <div class="form-demo">
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Work email</label>
              <input class="form-input" type="text" placeholder="you@company.com">
              <p class="form-helper">We'll only use this to send the deck.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label">Company name</label>
              <input class="form-input has-error" type="text" value="Acme">
              <p class="form-error-text">Please enter your full company name.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="form-group">
              <label class="form-label form-disabled-label">Referral code</label>
              <input class="form-input" type="text" placeholder="Optional" disabled>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="subsection" style="margin-bottom:0;">
        <p class="sub-label">8.6 — Meta / timestamp text</p>
        <p class="sub-desc">Quiet, small, out of the way — publish dates, last-updated stamps, byline-style detail.</p>
        <div class="util-card">
          <div class="meta-row">
            <span class="util-timestamp">Updated July 14, 2026</span>
            <span class="util-timestamp">6 min read</span>
            <span class="util-timestamp">BiomEdit Research Team</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section style="border-bottom:none;background:var(--bg-primary);">
    <div class="wrap">
      <div class="open-q">
        <h3>Open decisions before this is final</h3>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Fraunces' role.</strong> Intentionally left undecided for now — no assigned use in the system as it stands.</li>
          <li><strong>Sustainability color.</strong> Shown both ways above — Ember Orange (7.1) or Green (7.2). Which do you want to move forward with?</li>
          <li><strong>Dark theme scope.</strong> Tokens are defined, but still undecided whether dark mode extends to the Pipeline and content cards, or stays scoped to the marketing site's UI.</li>
          <li><strong>Specific color roles.</strong> All five brand colors now have filled/outline button treatments, and Deep Blue is set as the link color — but which color goes where on an actual page (category tags, status indicators, CTAs, data viz, etc.) is still to be worked out as real pages get designed.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>

<style>

    *{box-sizing:border-box;}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;}
  body{margin:0;background:var(--bg-primary);color:var(--text-primary);font-family:'PT Sans',sans-serif;-webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;}

  .meta-bar{background:#000;color:#fff;padding:14px 40px;font-size:13px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;}
  .meta-bar span{opacity:0.55;}

  section{padding:72px 40px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);background:var(--bg-primary);}
  .wrap{max-width:1180px;margin:0 auto;}

  .section-num{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;width:28px;height:28px;border-radius:50%;background:#000;color:#fff;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;margin-right:12px;flex-shrink:0;}
  .section-head{display:flex;align-items:center;margin-bottom:6px;}
  .section-head h2{font-size:26px;font-weight:700;margin:0;}
  .section-sub{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0 0 36px;max-width:680px;padding-left:40px;}

  .subsection{margin-bottom:56px;}
  .subsection:last-child{margin-bottom:0;}
  .sub-label{font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:700;color:var(--color-teal);margin:0 0 6px;}
  .sub-desc{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0 0 22px;max-width:620px;}

  .logo-strip{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:24px;padding:28px 40px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);background:var(--bg-secondary);}
  .logo-strip svg{height:28px;width:auto;}
  .logo-strip span{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-secondary);}

  /* swatches */
  .swatch-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:18px;border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:4px;padding:16px;background:var(--bg-secondary);}
  .swatch{width:56px;height:56px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;}
  .swatch-info .name{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;}
  .swatch-info .hex{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-tertiary);}
  .role-tag{margin-left:auto;font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.06em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-tertiary);border:1px solid var(--border-color);padding:4px 8px;border-radius:20px;}
  .color-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:16px;}

  /* neutral ramp */
  .ramp-strip9{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(9,1fr);border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;border:1px solid var(--border-color);}
  .ramp-swatch{aspect-ratio:0.9;display:flex;align-items:flex-end;padding:8px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;}
  .ramp-swatch .hex-lbl{display:block;opacity:0.7;font-size:9px;}

  /* token demo cards */
  .token-card{border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:6px;padding:24px;}
  .token-swatch-row{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;margin-bottom:10px;}
  .token-chip{width:40px;height:40px;border-radius:4px;flex-shrink:0;border:1px solid rgba(0,0,0,0.08);}
  .token-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;}
  .token-hex{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-tertiary);}
  .token-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;}

  /* dark theme demo panel */
  .dark-panel{background:var(--cool-900);border-radius:8px;padding:40px;}
  .dark-panel h3{color:var(--cool-100);font-size:20px;margin:0 0 8px;}
  .dark-panel p.body{color:var(--cool-300);font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 24px;max-width:480px;}
  .dark-token-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;margin-bottom:28px;}
  .dark-token-card{border-radius:6px;padding:18px;}
  .dark-accent-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:14px;}
  .dark-accent-chip{border-radius:6px;padding:16px 14px;}
  .dark-accent-chip .name{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--cool-900);}
  .dark-accent-chip .hex{font-size:11px;color:var(--cool-700);}

  /* type scale */
  .scale-row{display:flex;align-items:baseline;gap:24px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);padding:16px 0;}
  .scale-row:first-child{padding-top:0;}
  .scale-meta{width:140px;flex-shrink:0;font-size:12px;color:var(--text-tertiary);line-height:1.5;}
  .scale-meta .role{font-weight:700;color:var(--text-primary);display:block;font-size:13px;}
  .scale-sample{color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;font-weight:700;}
  .scale-sample.body-weight{font-weight:400;}

  /* content cards */
  .combo-card,.option-card,.para-card,.atom-card,.ui-card{border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:6px;background:var(--bg-secondary);}
  .combo-card{padding:36px;max-width:640px;}
  .combo-eyebrow{font-weight:700;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin:0 0 12px;}
  .combo-h{font-weight:700;font-size:34px;line-height:1.15;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 14px;}
  .combo-body{font-size:16px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;}

  .pair-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:20px;}
  .option-card{padding:26px 24px;}
  .option-name{font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-tertiary);font-weight:700;margin-bottom:16px;}
  .q-sample{border-left:3px solid var(--color-teal);padding-left:16px;}
  .q-sample p{font-size:19px;line-height:1.4;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0 0 8px;font-style:italic;}
  .q-sample cite{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-tertiary);font-style:normal;}
  .q-sample.fraunces p{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;}

  .para-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:24px;}
  .para-card{padding:28px;}
  .para-lead{font-weight:500;font-size:19px;line-height:1.55;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;}
  .para-standard{font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;}
  .para-dense{font-size:14px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text-primary);margin:0;}

  .caption-demo{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:10px;}
  .caption-swatch{width:100%;height:110px;border-radius:4px;object-fit:cover;display:block;}
  .caption-text{font-size:13px;color:var(--text-primary);font-style:italic;}
  .caption-text.fraunces{font-family:'Fraunces',serif;font-style:italic;font-weight:500;}

  .atom-row{display:flex;gap:20px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .atom-card{padding:22px 26px;}
  .eyebrow-demo{font-weight:700;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-primary);}

  .mini-logo{width:70px;height:15px;display:block;margin-bottom:12px;flex-shrink:0;}

  /* buttons/links */
  .ui-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:20px;}
  .ui-card{padding:32px 28px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;align-items:flex-start;}
  .ui-card-name{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;margin:0 0 -6px;}
  .ui-card-hex{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin:0 0 6px;}
  .ui-btn-filled{border:none;border-radius:4px;padding:12px 24px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;cursor:default;}
  .ui-btn-outline{background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:4px;padding:11px 23px;font-size:14px;font-weight:700;cursor:default;}
  .ui-link{font-size:14px;font-weight:600;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:3px;}

  /* pipeline */
  .pipeline-example{border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;background:var(--bg-secondary);}
  .pipeline-header{padding:24px 24px 20px;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:16px;background:var(--bg-tertiary);}
  .pipeline-title{font-weight:700;font-size:17px;margin:0;color:var(--text-primary);}
  .pipeline-tabs{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  input.tab-input{display:none;}
  .pipeline-tab{padding:7px 16px;border-radius:20px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;cursor:pointer;color:var(--text-secondary);background:var(--bg-secondary);border:1px solid var(--border-color);user-select:none;}
  .pipeline-tab[for$="-found"]{color:var(--color-teal);border-color:var(--color-teal);}
  .pipeline-tab[for$="-invest"]{color:var(--color-navy);border-color:var(--color-navy);}
  .pipeline-tab[for$="-break"]{color:var(--color-orange);border-color:var(--color-orange);}
  .pipeline-columns{display:flex;gap:1px;background:var(--border-color);overflow-x:auto;}
  .pipeline-col{background:var(--bg-tertiary);padding:16px 14px;min-width:170px;flex:1 0 170px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
  .stage-eyebrow{font-size:10px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.08em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin:0;}
  .pipeline-stage-head{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.02em;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:2px 0 4px;line-height:1.3;min-height:28px;}
  .pipeline-card{background:var(--bg-secondary);border-radius:6px;border-left:3px solid transparent;overflow:hidden;}
  .pipeline-card summary{list-style:none;cursor:pointer;padding:10px 12px;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:8px;}
  .pipeline-card summary::-webkit-details-marker{display:none;}
  .pipeline-card summary::marker{content:"";}
  .card-top-row{display:flex;align-items:flex-start;justify-content:space-between;gap:10px;width:100%;}
  .card-main{display:flex;flex-direction:column;}
  .pipeline-card .code{font-weight:700;font-size:13px;color:var(--text-primary);display:block;}
  .pipeline-card .focus{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin-top:2px;display:block;}
  .pipeline-card .chevron{flex-shrink:0;margin-top:3px;color:var(--text-tertiary);transition:transform 0.18s ease;}
  .pipeline-card[open] .chevron{transform:rotate(180deg);}
  .card-detail{padding:0 12px 14px;}
  .card-detail p{font-size:12px;line-height:1.6;color:var(--text-secondary);margin:0 0 8px;}
  .card-detail-link{font-size:12px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-primary);text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:2px;}
  .cat-foundational{border-left-color:var(--color-teal);}
  .cat-investigational{border-left-color:var(--color-navy);}
  .cat-breakthrough{border-left-color:var(--color-orange);}

  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-found:checked) .pipeline-card:not(.cat-foundational){display:none;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-invest:checked) .pipeline-card:not(.cat-investigational){display:none;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-break:checked) .pipeline-card:not(.cat-breakthrough){display:none;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-all:checked) label[for="pt-all"]{background:#000;color:#fff;border-color:#000;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-found:checked) label[for="pt-found"]{background:var(--color-teal);color:#fff;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-invest:checked) label[for="pt-invest"]{background:var(--color-navy);color:#fff;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt-break:checked) label[for="pt-break"]{background:var(--color-orange);color:#fff;}

  /* second pipeline: sustainability shown in green instead of orange */
  .sustain-green .cat-breakthrough{border-left-color:var(--color-green);}
  .sustain-green .pipeline-tab[for$="-break"]{color:var(--color-green);border-color:var(--color-green);}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-found:checked) .pipeline-card:not(.cat-foundational){display:none;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-invest:checked) .pipeline-card:not(.cat-investigational){display:none;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-break:checked) .pipeline-card:not(.cat-breakthrough){display:none;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-all:checked) label[for="pt2-all"]{background:#000;color:#fff;border-color:#000;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-found:checked) label[for="pt2-found"]{background:var(--color-teal);color:#fff;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-invest:checked) label[for="pt2-invest"]{background:var(--color-navy);color:#fff;}
  .pipeline-example:has(#pt2-break:checked) label[for="pt2-break"]{background:var(--color-green);color:#fff;}

  /* open questions callout */
  .open-q{background:#FFF7E6;border:1px solid var(--color-amber);border-radius:8px;padding:28px 32px;}
  .open-q h3{margin:0 0 12px;font-size:16px;color:#7A4A00;}
  .open-q ol{margin:0;padding-left:20px;color:#7A4A00;font-size:14px;line-height:1.8;}

  /* utility text styles */
  .util-card{border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:6px;padding:24px 28px;background:var(--bg-secondary);}
  .util-overline{font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin:0;}

  .util-table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;}
  .util-table th{text-align:left;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:0.04em;color:var(--text-tertiary);padding:10px 12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);}
  .util-table td{font-size:14px;color:var(--text-primary);padding:12px;border-bottom:1px solid var(--border-color);}
  .util-table tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none;}

  .data-pair-row{display:flex;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .data-pair{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px;}
  .util-data-label{font-weight:700;font-size:14px;color:var(--text-primary);}
  .util-meta{font-size:11px;color:var(--text-tertiary);}

  .badge-row{display:flex;gap:10px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .util-badge{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.04em;text-transform:uppercase;padding:6px 14px;border-radius:20px;}

  .form-demo{display:flex;gap:32px;flex-wrap:wrap;}
  .form-group{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:6px;max-width:280px;flex:1 1 260px;}
  .form-label{font-size:13px;font-weight:700;color:var(--text-primary);}
  .form-input{font-family:'PT Sans',sans-serif;font-size:14px;padding:10px 12px;border:1px solid var(--border-color);border-radius:4px;background:var(--bg-secondary);color:var(--text-primary);}
  .form-input::placeholder{color:var(--text-tertiary);}
  .form-helper{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-tertiary);margin:0;}
  .form-input.has-error{border-color:var(--color-amber);}
  .form-error-text{font-size:12px;color:var(--color-amber);font-weight:600;margin:0;}
  .form-input:disabled{opacity:0.5;cursor:not-allowed;}
  .form-disabled-label{opacity:0.5;}

  .meta-row{display:flex;gap:28px;flex-wrap:wrap;align-items:baseline;}
  .util-timestamp{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-tertiary);}

  @media (max-width:900px){
    .color-grid,.token-grid,.pair-grid,.para-grid,.ui-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;}
    .dark-token-grid,.dark-accent-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);}
    .ramp-strip9{grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);}
    .scale-row{flex-direction:column;gap:6px;}
    .scale-meta{width:auto;}
    .section-sub{padding-left:0;}
  }

  .sg-intro { max-width: 900px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 60px 40px 0; }
  .sg-intro .overline { margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .sg-intro h1 { font-size: 32px; margin: 0 0 16px; }
  .sg-intro p:last-child { font-size: 15px; line-height: 1.7; color: var(--text-secondary); max-width: 640px; }
</style>
